snippet.title: CBSE Class KG | English |  Story Telling | Two friends and the bear |
snippet.description:
In this lesson, you learn about, Storytelling two friends and the bear,
Once upon a time long long ago in a village they lived two friends.
Their names were Sujith and Ajith.
One day they had a holiday at school.
So they decided to go in to a forest that was near than village.
While they were happily walking along to the forest 
Suddenly a bear appeared in front of them.
He thinks to come out the nowhere!
Both of them were very scared.
Oh my goodness! this bear is huge! 
Ajith knew how to climb a tree.
So he quickly ran up to a nearby tree and climbed up.
He was so scared looking at the bear that he forgot about who was Sujith.
Poor Sujith was left on alone
Sujith did not even know how to climbed tree.
What was he did do?
Sujith thought heart
He remembered reading somewhere that animals did not like dead bodies.
This gives him an Idea.
He immediately felt the ground and held is breath. 
The bear came right near Sujith she sniffed Sujith all over
They thought that Sujith was dead.
So it walked away. 
Once the bear was out of sight Sujith got up.
Both the boys were the relieved that the bear went away.
Ajith climb down the tree.
He asked Sujith what did the bear whisper the ears.
Bear told me to keep away that friends like you said Sujith
Moral of the Story:
So remember Children 
A friend in need is a friend indeed.

snippet.title: CBSE Class KG | English | Words | Two - letter words |
snippet.description:
In this lesson, you learn about, Two letter words

A e i o u
Welcome to the two letter word land. Look who we have hear. Our vowel friends. A, e, i, o and u. They are going to make new friends here. Let's go see their new friends.
A d g m n p s t
Hello mr. A . How many friends have you made today. Oh, quite a few. Their is d when we are seen together we are called ad. A and d is ad. Then their is g when we are seen together we are called ag. A and g is ag. Then I met m when we are seen together we are called am. A and m is am. Then n became my friend. When we are seen together we are called an. A and n is an. Then their is p. When we are seen together we are called ap. A and p is ap. Then their is s. When we are seen together we are called as. A and s is as. Finally he also became my friend. When we are seen together we are called at. A and t is at. Wow mr. A. You have made so many two letter friends.
E d g n t
Let's go see mr. E's friends now. Hello mr. E. How many friends have you made today. Hello I made a few friends. Their is d when we are seen together we are called ed. E and d is ed. 
Then their is g when we are seen together we are called eg. E and g is eg. N is also my friend. When we are seen together we are called en. E and n is en. Then t became my friend. When we are seen together we are called et. E and t is Et. Wow mr. E. You have made so many two letter friends.
I b d g m n p t
Let's now go and see mr. I's friends now. Hello mr. I. How many friends have you made today. Ho quite a few. Their is b  when we are seen together we are called ib. I and b is ib. Then their is d  when we are seen together we are called id. I and d is id. G is also become my friend.  When we are seen together we are called ig. I and g is ig. Then their is m  when we are seen together we are called im. I and m is im. N also became my friend.  When we are seen together we are called in. I and n is in. Then their is p.  When we are seen together we are called ip. I and p is ip. Finally t also became my friend.  When we are seen together we are called it. I and t is it.  Wow mr. I. You have made so many two letter friends.
O d g p t x y
Let's go see mr. O's friends now. Hello mr. O. How many friends have you made today.  Hello I made a few friends. Their is d when we are seen together we are called ad. O and d is od. Then their is g when we are seen together we are called og. O and g is og. P is also my friend now. when we are seen together we are called op. O and p is op. Then their is t when we are seen together we are called ot. O and t is ot. X is also my friend now. when we are seen together we are called ox. O and x is ox. Then their is y. When we are seen together we are called oy. O and y is oy. Wow mr. O. You have made so many two letter friends.
U b d g m n p t
Let's go see mr. U's friends now. Hello mr. U. How many friends have you made today. Ho quite a few.  Their is b when we are seen together we are called ub. U and b is ub.  Then their is d  when we are seen together we are called ud. U and d is ud.  G also my friend now. When we are seen together we are called ug. U and g is ug. M also became my friend. When we are seen together we are called um. U and m is um. Then their is un. When we are seen together we are called un. U and n is un. Their is p. When we are seen together we are called up. U and p is up. T is also my friend now. When we are seen together we are called ut. U and t is ut.  Wow mr. U. You have made so many friends.
Wasn't that fun children. We have learnt so many two letter words today after meeting our vowel friends.
